text:
@venturetwins It’s just a “large model” at this point, not a large language model, as the new models are all multimodal.

Video (with sound) will be a supermajority of the byte count.

Also, we should think of models in terms of Gigabytes, not parameters, given heavy use of int4 &amp; fp4.

